<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>
    <FactionDef>
        <defName>WNA_FactionWNA</defName>
        <label>Whellingnorther Alliance</label>
        <categoryTag>WNA_FactionWNA</categoryTag>
        <factionIconPath>factions/wna_alliance</factionIconPath>
        <settlementTexturePath>karma</settlementTexturePath>
        <description>Thousands of years ago they rose from a remote planet where people suffers from conflicts and oppression, since then they have spread their activities across the known universe, mysterious as ghosts and omnipresent as shades. These black-hooded figure and the Whelingnorther Humanoid Revolt under their command have brought death and horror to almost everywhere they reached. This cult itself is relatively young but actually their origin is far more ancient, even older than the universe.\n\nThis branch of Whelingnorther Alliance have settled on this rimworld for a long time. Although they appear to be peaceful at the moment, they have undoubtedly had plenty of violent conflicts with other factions on the planet. Recently they seem to be becoming active again and preparing to achieve their ultimate goal - the Whelingnorther Apocalypse.</description>
        <pawnSingular>follower</pawnSingular>
        <pawnsPlural>followers</pawnsPlural>
